               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17860426-110-cd500" type="crimeDate">26th day of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860426-110-off499 t17860426-110-cd500"></join>, one blue and white printed curtain, value 26 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
